rComments: Tough class, but he'll help you make it. Presents course material in an interesting way, even though he likes to get into proofs and theory a little too much.

He explains things really well and his lectures a very organized. He writes all of the notes on the chalkboard and doesn't post anything online so attending class is a must. Homework and exams are fair. Overall the best CHBE professor I've had thus far.
Solid Professor. Possible to get an A in the class as long as you go to office hours and class. Study the homework well, his exams are based off the homework.
Amazing professor especially if you seek out help to ask concepts. Class notes/ lectures extremely helpful and relevant.
Explains super well, but hard tests
